item.description:
I've updated luajit, following a recommendation from Julian Grinblat,
to fix a problem with neovim. I haven't encountered this problem,
but if you can test programs that need luajit I'd appreciate it.
I also apologize for the enormous delay with which I replied to the
reports on github, unfortunately I do not receive notifications or
report emails.
It will be my care in the future to manually check the reports.
As always I apologize for my bad English.
Thank you all.
